/> <br />\n然後一踏入個出入口仲要俾個風閘閘一閘，行到埋個入口唔夠一步當堂有種歡迎進入地獄嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入到地鐵有細路又嘈又喐黎喐去又迫又要俾啲廢老推黎推去又沖閘，跟著度門又例牌咁閂幾次先閂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出咗地鐵站又有死煙鏟又有汽車廢氣又要瘋狂紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本未到公司都未可以呼吸一啖比較乾淨嘅空氣同比較舒適嘅空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔好話香港人點解成日留係公司，我地唔係鐘意工作，而只係唔想再面對放工脫苦海後翻屋企前嘅油鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdb6299706a0d64d3d4b21fa11141052aa8a8d6","tid":901864,"uid":131262,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:40:55.000Z","msg":"紅磡站：365日都係炎夏"},{"pid":"9b5a544e757201e35f5456764d4b64261cac9970","tid":901864,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"涼少少地鐵就唔開冷氣有病"},{"pid":"fc44a4f269b3e1b3caf60cf0be10bfde00929c73","tid":901864,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"083bedc5cd6581a2b05405f5e58ef2e54bed47c6","tid":901864,"uid":36026,"like":662,"dislike":2,"score":660,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"外面10度果陣著件短袖tee喺地鐵站都會流汗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n個時係北京坐地鐵地面零下幾度<br />\n我都係咁出汗"},{"pid":"d46618d29bc961dc9c75d0e3636249ee84faebaa","tid":901864,"uid":2923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味年年都慳皮慳到盡,抽風都唔撚做,每次地鐵事故塞爆人都焗撚到暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7cb88c1dde7d046ad9696e57e213c50aca5307","tid":901864,"uid":96767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"問過上環站未<img src=\"/assets/face